    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car shows clear signs of age, including several cosmetic blemishes like minor dents, paint fading on the hood, and some interior wear on the driver's seat. It has been maintained regularly, though it will likely need minor suspension work in the near future. Overall, it is a solid, functional vehicle that provides great value for its price.",
