    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, preserved in pristine mechanical condition. This example features the legendary 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six engine, utilizing its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration and air-to-air intercooler for optimal volumetric efficiency. Power is managed via the Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through a factory-spec helical limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its rigorous double-wishbone suspension geometry, with all bushings and dampers exhibiting factory-level compliance. The engine bay is a testament to meticulous maintenance, with zero evidence of fluid weeping or thermal fatigue on the vacuum lines. The original paint maintains its factory depth, and the undercarriage remains free of oxidation. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically pure, unmodified specimen that performs exactly as engineered by Toyota\u2019s performance division.",
